{"type": "article", "id": 13997, "title": "Type75 台灯第二版", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-26T07:50:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000259LeubECXnjcON4lp2.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tPaul Smith 和 Anglepoise 合作的 Type75 台灯最近推出了第二版，设计延续了 Paul Smith 标志性的彩条灯柱，加上这款 20 世纪最为经典的台灯外形，自然一点差错都没有，相对第一版明快的配色，这次的颜色选择了沉稳的深色系，时尚的同时经典又充满风情。台灯售价 270 美元，将会在 9 月底面市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141644rJKGm9tlIRd5vahW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<span></span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141645dDz9ab1vqeSs0RIJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141645iwWSmq4Oo7VY9M3u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n\n\n\n"}